{"tid":1482612,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"想改變一個大陸朋友既諗法！！文宣唔該幫手！！","createTime":"2019-08-18T06:40:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T14:41:19.000Z","uid":206306,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"47370d4d883ef4568c7938d7fc009451626957cf","tid":1482612,"uid":206306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T06:40:16.000Z","msg":"我有個住外國 有埋外國國籍既同學 密切關注緊香港既事 佢係喺外國香港人集會入面舉中國旗既on9之一 我有問佢點解要咁做 佢話佢不嬲反共產黨（呢個我都知） 但係話接受唔到我地舉港英旗 擺明係想港獨咁 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">不過</span> 喺我不斷勸說下佢都想聆聽我地既聲音 唔係一面倒打擊香港 佢都好心痛 甚至想黎香港親身感受下 佢唔係嗰啲盲反既大陸人 呢個我可以肯定 佢只係想兩邊既聲音都聽<br />\n<br />\n佢send左啲乜中國加油既微信group對話比我睇<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LiVegr7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLiVegr7.jpg&h=2737691a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KTjKDFt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKTjKDFt.jpg&h=b7c37ddc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後佢send多條link比我話係佢覺得喺牆內條件入面「最貼近事實」既文章 話喺牆內瘋傳緊<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/p5gCdU6Zxz4Q-EWtADT-_A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmp.weixin.qq.com%2Fs%2Fp5gCdU6Zxz4Q-EWtADT-_A&d=MqHS405OUPR0rJ167hdmPNLD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=f24f5e4b\" target=\"_blank\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/p5gCdU6Zxz4Q-EWtADT-_A</a></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁當然入面都係屌鳩示威者 話外國勢力入侵嗰啲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/62FxNzn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F62FxNzn.png&h=a73286d7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DA8zgsK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDA8zgsK.png&h=9067f82d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XSUq7zt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXSUq7zt.png&h=d4fddd9d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/svTrR09.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsvTrR09.png&h=345dddb1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jVob27R.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjVob27R.png&h=bc8dd6fd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/18/143452_fb7a6e7650b2ac2cb1dc84f9b34971eb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F18%2F143452_fb7a6e7650b2ac2cb1dc84f9b34971eb.png&h=8d769fcb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個大陸朋友需要既係理據去一一攻破呢啲所謂既事實 我口才不好所以我想請各位幫我突破嗰篇文章既盲點 同埋點樣可以令佢明白香港人做既一切<br />\n<br />\n願意聆聽既大陸人已經買少見少 我希望如果改變到佢既話佢會嘗試改變埋其他接收緊牆內資訊既大陸人 大家見到可唔可以幫幫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">維園見！！未黎快啲黎！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"3ef451dcb8c359dd4c0a3a2ffe7ba729f0c59420","tid":1482612,"uid":206306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T06:41:01.000Z","msg":"Ji tui<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c856067a27975cc57bb49cc1a328a93679b2002","tid":1482612,"uid":206306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T06:41:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1eab2f6d451613e06917322b5da9f1ad0c1b1ab9","tid":1482612,"uid":206306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T06:42:28.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2c6c24d11aac33f0d476330a4a17ad0cea4d16c","ti